    "viewsContainers": {
      "activitybar": [
        {
          "id": "snapback",
          "title": "SnapBack",
          "icon": "media/activitybar-icon-24.png"
        }
      ]
    },
    "views": {
      "snapback": [
        {
          "id": "snapback.dashboard",
          "name": "SnapBack",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && config.snapback.ui.showTreeView",
          "icon": "$(shield)"
        },
        {
          "id": "snapback.intelligence",
          "name": "Intelligence",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && config.snapback.ui.showTreeView",
          "icon": "$(warning)"
        },
        {
          "id": "snapback.sessions",
          "name": "Sessions",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && config.snapback.ui.showTreeView"
        }
      ]
    },
    "submenus": [
      {
        "id": "snapback.protectFile",
        "label": "SnapBack: Protect File"
      },
      {
        "id": "snapback.changeProtectionLevel",
        "label": "SnapBack: Change Protection Level"
      }
    ],
    "menus": {
      "explorer/context": [
        {
          "command": "snapback.createSnapshot",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && !explorerResourceIsFolder",
          "group": "snapback@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.snapBack",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && !explorerResourceIsFolder",
          "group": "snapback@2"
        },
        {
          "submenu": "snapback.protectFile",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && !explorerResourceIsFolder && !snapback.isProtected",
          "group": "snapback@3"
        },
        {
          "submenu": "snapback.changeProtectionLevel",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && !explorerResourceIsFolder && snapback.isProtected",
          "group": "snapback@3"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.unprotectFile",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && !explorerResourceIsFolder && snapback.isProtected",
          "group": "snapback@3"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.compareWithSnapshot",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && !explorerResourceIsFolder",
          "group": "snapback@4"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.createPolicyOverride",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && !explorerResourceIsFolder",
          "group": "snapback@5"
        }
      ],
      "snapback.protectFile": [
        {
          "command": "snapback.setWatchLevel",
          "group": "levels@1",
          "when": "snapback.canProtect"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.setWarnLevel",
          "group": "levels@2",
          "when": "snapback.canProtect"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.setBlockLevel",
          "group": "levels@3",
          "when": "snapback.canProtect"
        }
      ],
      "snapback.changeProtectionLevel": [
        {
          "command": "snapback.setWatchLevel",
          "group": "levels@1",
          "when": "snapback.isProtected && snapback.currentLevel != 'watch'"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.setWarnLevel",
          "group": "levels@2",
          "when": "snapback.isProtected && snapback.currentLevel != 'warn'"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.setBlockLevel",
          "group": "levels@3",
          "when": "snapback.isProtected && snapback.currentLevel != 'block'"
        }
      ],
      "editor/context": [
        {
          "submenu": "snapback.protectFile",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && !snapback.isProtected",
          "group": "snapback@1"
        },
        {
          "submenu": "snapback.changeProtectionLevel",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && snapback.isProtected",
          "group": "snapback@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.unprotectFile",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && snapback.isProtected",
          "group": "snapback@2"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.createSnapshot",
          "when": "snapback.isActive",
          "group": "snapback@3"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.createPolicyOverride",
          "when": "snapback.isActive",
          "group": "snapback@4"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.toggleOfflineMode",
          "when": "snapback.isActive",
          "group": "snapback@5"
        }
      ],
      "commandPalette": [
        {
          "command": "snapback.protectFile",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && editorFocus"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.protectCurrentFile",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && editorFocus"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.changeProtectionLevel",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && editorFocus"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.setWatchLevel",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && editorFocus"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.setWarnLevel",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && editorFocus"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.setBlockLevel",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && editorFocus"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.unprotectFile",
          "when": "snapback.isActive && snapback.fileProtected"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.compareWithSnapshot",
          "when": "snapback.isActive"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.openProtectedFile",
          "when": "false"
        }
      ],
      "view/item/context": [
        {
          "command": "snapback.openProtectedFile",
          "when": "view == snapback.protectedFiles && viewItem == snapback.item.protectedFile",
          "group": "navigation@1"
        },
        {
          "submenu": "snapback.changeProtectionLevel",
          "when": "view == snapback.protectedFiles && viewItem == snapback.item.protectedFile",
          "group": "protection@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.createSnapshot",
          "when": "view == snapback.protectedFiles && viewItem == snapback.item.protectedFile",
          "group": "snapshot@1",
          "icon": "$(save)"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.snapBack",
          "when": "view == snapback.protectedFiles && viewItem == snapback.item.protectedFile",
          "group": "snapshot@2",
          "icon": "$(history)"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.unprotectFile",
          "when": "view == snapback.protectedFiles && viewItem == snapback.item.protectedFile",
          "group": "danger@1",
          "icon": "$(unlock)"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.unprotectFile",
          "when": "view == snapback.main && viewItem == snapback.item.protectedFile",
          "group": "danger@1",
          "icon": "$(unlock)"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.openSnapshotInWeb",
          "when": "view == snapbackExplorer && viewItem == snapshot",
          "group": "navigation@1",
          "icon": "$(link-external)"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.createSnapshot",
          "when": "view == snapbackExplorer && viewItem == blockingIssue",
          "group": "snapshot@1",
          "icon": "$(save)"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.snapshot.showFileDiff",
          "when": "view == snapback.dashboard && viewItem == activityEventSingle",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.snapshot.showFileDiff",
          "when": "view == snapback.dashboard && viewItem == activityFile",
          "group": "inline"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.restoreSnapshot",
          "when": "view == snapback.dashboard && viewItem =~ /^activityEvent/",
          "group": "inline@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.deleteSnapshot",
          "when": "view == snapback.dashboard && viewItem =~ /^activityEvent/",
          "group": "inline@2"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.restoreSnapshot",
          "when": "view == snapback.dashboard && viewItem =~ /^activityEvent/",
          "group": "snapshot@1"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.deleteSnapshot",
          "when": "view == snapback.dashboard && viewItem =~ /^activityEvent/",
          "group": "danger@1"
        }
      ],
      "view/title": [
        {
          "command": "snapback.session.restore",
          "when": "view == snapback.dashboard",
          "group": "navigation@1",
          "icon": "$(debug-step-back)"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.createSnapshot",
          "when": "view == snapback.dashboard",
          "group": "navigation@2",
          "icon": "$(save)"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.showAllSnapshots",
          "when": "view == snapback.dashboard",
          "group": "navigation@3",
          "icon": "$(archive)"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.refreshViews",
          "when": "view == snapback.dashboard",
          "group": "navigation@4",
          "icon": "$(refresh)"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.showStatus",
          "when": "view == snapback.dashboard && snapback.protectionStatus == complete",
          "group": "navigation@5",
          "icon": "$(shield-check)"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.protectEntireRepo",
          "when": "view == snapback.dashboard && snapback.protectionStatus != complete",
          "group": "navigation@6"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.refreshViews",
          "when": "view == snapback.protectedFiles",
          "group": "navigation@1",
          "icon": "$(refresh)"
        },
        {
          "command": "snapback.showAllProtectedFiles",
          "when": "view == snapback.protectedFiles",
          "group": "navigation@2",
          "icon": "$(list-tree)"
        }
      ]
    },
    "configuration": {
      "title": "SnapBack",
      "properties": {
        "snapback.aiDetection.enabled": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "markdownDescription": "**Enable AI Detection**\n\nDetects AI-generated code changes and creates automatic protection snapshots.",
          "order": 1
        },
        "snapback.showAutoSnapshotNotifications": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "markdownDescription": "**Show Snapshot Notifications**\n\nDisplay brief notifications when auto-snapshots are created.",
          "order": 2
        },
        "snapback.guardian.enabled": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "markdownDescription": "**Enable Guardian**\n\nProtects against risky code patterns: secrets, mock replacements, phantom dependencies.",
          "order": 3
        },
        "snapback.proactiveAlerts.enabled": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "markdownDescription": "**Enable Proactive Alerts**\n\nGenerates contextual alerts when editing protected or critical files (.env, auth, secrets). Alerts are exposed via MCP for LLM consumption.",
          "order": 4
        },
        "snapback.mcp.enabled": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "markdownDescription": "**Enable MCP Integration**\n\nAllows AI assistants (Claude, Cursor, Windsurf) to interact with SnapBack.",
          "order": 4
        },
        "snapback.mcp.serverUrl": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "https://snapback-mcp.fly.dev",
          "markdownDescription": "**MCP Server URL**\n\nURL for the remote MCP server. Leave default for cloud, or set to local server.",
          "order": 5
        },
        "snapback.offlineMode.enabled": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": false,
          "markdownDescription": "**Offline Mode**\n\nDisable all network requests. Snapshots work locally only.",
          "order": 6
        },
        "snapback.logLevel": {
          "type": "string",
          "enum": [
            "silent",
            "error",
            "warn",
            "info",
            "debug",
            "trace"
          ],
          "default": "info",
          "markdownDescription": "**Log Level**\n\nFor troubleshooting. Set to `debug` for verbose output, `trace` for maximum detail, or `silent` to disable all logging.",
          "order": 7
        },
        "snapback.logNamespaces": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": [
              "activation",
              "mcp",
              "snapshot",
              "protection",
              "auth",
              "daemon",
              "storage",
              "telemetry"
            ]
          },
          "default": [],
          "markdownDescription": "**Log Namespaces**\n\nFilter debug logs to specific subsystems. Empty means all subsystems log at the configured level. Example: `[\"activation\", \"mcp\"]` to only see debug logs from those modules.",
          "order": 8
        },
        "snapback.logBatchDebug": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": false,
          "markdownDescription": "**Batch Debug Logs**\n\nAggregate high-frequency debug logs into batched summaries. Reduces Output channel noise during intensive operations.",
          "order": 9
        },
        "snapback.ui.showTreeView": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": false,
          "markdownDescription": "**Show Sidebar Tree View**\n\nEnable the full SnapBack tree view in the Activity Bar. When off, uses minimal status bar UI.",
          "order": 8
        },
        "snapback.ui.hideInternalFiles": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "markdownDescription": "**Hide Internal Files**\n\nHide `.snapback/` directory contents in VS Code explorer. Internal files are implementation details users don't need to see.",
          "order": 9
        },
        "snapback.mcp.autoEnable": {
          "type": "boolean",
          "default": true,
          "markdownDescription": "**Auto-Configure MCP**\n\nAutomatically configure MCP for detected AI assistants (Cursor, Claude Desktop, Windsurf) on extension activation.",
          "order": 10
        }
      }
    },
    "configurationDefaults": {
      "files.exclude": {
        "**/.snapback": true
      }
    },
    "keybindings": [
      {
        "command": "snapback.protectFile",
        "key": "ctrl+alt+p",
        "mac": "cmd+alt+p",
        "when": "editorFocus"
      },
      {
        "command": "snapback.createSnapshot",
        "key": "ctrl+alt+s",
        "mac": "cmd+alt+s",
        "when": "editorFocus"
      },
      {
        "command": "snapback.snapBack",
        "key": "ctrl+alt+z",
        "mac": "cmd+alt+z"
      },
      {
        "command": "snapback.deleteSnapshot",
        "key": "delete",
        "when": "focusedView == snapback.main && viewItem == snapshot"
      },
      {
        "command": "snapback.renameSnapshot",
        "key": "f2",
        "when": "focusedView == snapback.main && viewItem == snapshot"
      },
      {
        "command": "snapback.quickRestore",
        "key": "ctrl+shift+r",
        "mac": "cmd+shift+r"
      }
    ],
    "walkthroughs": [
      {
        "id": "snapback.welcome",
        "title": "Get Started with SnapBack",
        "description": "Get protected in 2 minutes. No configuration needed.",
        "steps": [
          {
            "id": "snapback.already-protected",
            "title": "You're Already Protected",
            "description": "SnapBack starts protecting you automatically.\n\n✅ **Automatic snapshots** on every save\n✅ **AI detection** for Cursor, Copilot, Claude, Windsurf\n✅ **Local storage** - your code never leaves your machine\n\nNo configuration needed. Just save a file and you're protected.",
            "media": {
              "markdown": "## How SnapBack Works\n\nSnapBack uses an intelligent AutoDecisionEngine to protect your code:\n\n### What Triggers a Snapshot?\n- AI tool made changes (89% detection accuracy)\n- Critical files modified (.env, auth, config)\n- High-risk change patterns detected\n- Multiple files changed rapidly\n\n### Privacy First\n- All snapshots stored locally in `~/.snapback`\n- No cloud uploads by default\n- Works completely offline\n- No account required"
            }
          },
          {
            "id": "snapback.make-first-save",
            "title": "See It Work",
            "description": "Open any file and save it.\n\n1. Make a small change\n2. Save the file (`Cmd+S` or `Ctrl+S`)\n3. Look for the 🧢 icon in the status bar\n\n**What happened:**\n- SnapBack captured a snapshot automatically\n- Status bar updated with snapshot count\n- Timeline entry created for recovery\n\n[Open a file to try it](command:workbench.action.quickOpen)",
            "media": {
              "markdown": "## SnapBack Status Bar\n\nLook for the 🧢 icon in your status bar:\n\n- **🧢 Protected** - SnapBack is active\n- **🧢 Snapshot saved** - Just created a restore point\n- **🧢 AI detected** - AI change captured\n\n### Performance\n- Snapshots take <100ms\n- No editor lag\n- Sub-2MB extension bundle"
            },
            "completionEvents": [
              "onCommand:snapback.createSnapshot"
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "snapback.restore-snapshot",
            "title": "Restore a Snapshot",
            "description": "Something went wrong? Restore in one click.\n\n**Option 1: Quick Restore**\n- Press `Cmd+Alt+Z` (Mac) or `Ctrl+Alt+Z` (Windows)\n- Instantly restore the last snapshot\n\n**Option 2: Browse & Restore**\n- Click the 🧢 status bar icon\n- Select a snapshot from the list\n- Click \"Restore\"\n\n[Try Quick Restore](command:snapback.snapBack)",
            "media": {
              "markdown": "## One-Click Recovery\n\nWhen AI overwrites your code:\n\n1. **Don't panic** - SnapBack has your back\n2. Press `Cmd+Alt+Z` / `Ctrl+Alt+Z`\n3. Your file is restored in <100ms\n\n### Keyboard Shortcuts\n- `Cmd+Alt+Z` - Snap Back (Restore)\n- `Cmd+Alt+S` - Create Manual Snapshot\n- `Cmd+Shift+R` - Quick Restore Picker\n\n💡 **Pro Tip:** Use Quick Restore Picker to choose exactly which version to restore."
            },
            "completionEvents": [
              "onCommand:snapback.snapBack",
              "onCommand:snapback.restoreLastSnapshot"
            ]
          },
          {
            "id": "snapback.explore-timeline",
            "title": "Browse Your Timeline",
            "description": "View your complete session history:\n\n1. Click the SnapBack icon (🧢) in the Activity Bar\n2. Browse snapshots by time or file\n3. Compare any snapshot with current state\n4. Restore any point where things worked\n\n[Open SnapBack Panel](command:workbench.view.extension.snapback)",
            "media": {
              "markdown": "## Session Timeline\n\nThe SnapBack panel shows:\n\n### Activity View\n- All snapshots in chronological order\n- AI-detected changes highlighted\n- Quick diff and restore actions\n\n### Session Groups\n- Related changes grouped together\n- Multi-file restores for AI refactoring sessions\n- See the full context of what changed\n\n### Keyboard Shortcuts\n- `Cmd+Alt+S` / `Ctrl+Alt+S` - Create Snapshot\n- `Cmd+Alt+Z` / `Ctrl+Alt+Z` - Snap Back\n- `Cmd+Shift+R` / `Ctrl+Shift+R` - Quick Restore Picker"
            },
            "completionEvents": [
              "onView:snapback.dashboard"
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
    "viewsWelcome": [
      {
        "view": "snapback.protectedFiles",
        "contents": "No snapshots yet.\n\nSnapBack creates snapshots automatically when you save files.\n\n[🧢 Create Manual Snapshot](command:snapback.createSnapshot)\n\nLearn more in [Getting Started](command:snapback.openWalkthrough).",
        "when": "!snapback.hasProtectedFiles"
      }
    ],
    "jsonValidation": [
      {
        "fileMatch": ".snapbackrc",
        "url": "./schemas/snapbackrc.schema.json"
      }
    ]
  },
